'''里武·拉库图沃'''（{{lang-mg|Rivo Rakotovao}}，{{bd|1960年|5月12日}}）是[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]]政治家，2018年至2019年担任[[马达加斯加国家元首列表|马达加斯加代理总统]]。此外，拉库图沃还担任马达加斯加参议院议长。<ref name="xinhuanet">{{Cite web|title=Madagascar's president resigns from post to participate in new election - Xinhua | English.news.cn|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2018-09/08/c_137452831.htm|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=xinhuanet.com}}</ref><ref name="theeastafrican">{{Cite web|title=Madagascar president resigns ahead of November poll|url=https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/news/africa/Madagascar-president-resigns-/4552902-4749800-cef07nz/index.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=The East African|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705170440/https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/news/africa/Madagascar-president-resigns-/4552902-4749800-cef07nz/index.html|archive-date=2020-07-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 

== 马达加斯加代理总统 ==
2018年9月7日，总统[[埃里·拉乔纳里马曼皮亚尼纳|埃里·拉乔纳里马曼皮亚尼纳]]递交了总统辞呈，这是法律要求他参加即将举行的[[2018年马达加斯加总统选举|总统选举]]的行为。参议院议长拉库图沃担任代理总统一职，直到选举中当选总统的[[安德里·拉乔利纳|安德里·拉乔利纳]]就职<ref name="xinhuanet">{{Cite web|title=Madagascar's president resigns from post to participate in new election - Xinhua | English.news.cn|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2018-09/08/c_137452831.htm|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=xinhuanet.com}}</ref><ref name="theeastafrican">{{Cite web|title=Madagascar president resigns ahead of November poll|url=https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/news/africa/Madagascar-president-resigns-/4552902-4749800-cef07nz/index.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=The East African|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705170440/https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/news/africa/Madagascar-president-resigns-/4552902-4749800-cef07nz/index.html|archive-date=2020-07-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="madagascar-tribune">{{Cite web|title=Mananjara Andriambololona succède à Rivo Rakotovao|url=https://www.madagascar-tribune.com/Mananjara-Andriambololona-succede,24233.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=Madagascar-Tribune.com}}</ref><ref name="ipreunion">{{Cite web|title=Pour briguer un nouveau mandat : Madagascar : le Président de la République a démissionné | Imaz Press Réunion : l'actualité de la Réunion en photos|url=http://www.ipreunion.com/actualites-reunion/reportage/2018/09/08/la-constitution-l-y-contraint-pour-briguer-un-nouveau-mandat-madagascar-le-president-de-la-republique-a-demissionne,90274.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=ipreunion.com}}</ref>。9月9日，[[联合国|联合国]]秘书长[[安东尼奥·古特雷斯|安东尼奥·古特雷斯]]重申他对拉库图沃的支持<ref name="un">{{Cite web|title=Madagascar: UN Secretary-General reaffirms support for electoral process | UN News|url=https://news.un.org/en/story/2018/09/1018821|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=news.un.org}}</ref>。2022 年 6 月 14 日，Rivo Rakotovao 因涉嫌腐败、挪用公款和滥用职权被独立反腐败办公室传唤。[https://www.rfi.fr/fr/afrique/20220614-madagascar-l-ex-pr%C3%A9sident-du-s%C3%A9nat-rivo-rakotovao-devant-la-justice-pour-corruption]

